      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this meticulously preserved specimen. Presented in showroom-quality condition, this vehicle boasts a flawless exterior and a cabin that remains indistinguishable from new. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than the absolute best, this offering represents a rare opportunity to own a truly investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
